cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Synesis: A DSL compiler for knowledge engineering"
abstract: >
  synesis-lsp is the Language Server Protocol implementation for the Synesis DSL.
  It provides real-time diagnostics, hover documentation, code completion, go-to-definition,
  find references, rename, semantic tokens, inlay hints, and ontology annotations
  directly in the editor as the researcher annotates.
authors:
